      <h2 class="mt-4">Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>User registration: Allows users to create a new account with a unique username and password.</li>
        <li>User login: Provides a secure login mechanism to authenticate users and grant access to protected areas.
        </li>
        <li>Password hashing: Uses advanced cryptographic algorithms to securely hash and store user passwords.</li>
        <li>Sign in with Google: Enables users to sign in using their Google accounts for a seamless authentication
          experience.</li>
        <li>Update password securely: Allows users to change their passwords securely with proper validation and
          authentication.</li>
        <li>Cookie management: Utilizes cookies to store session information and enhance user experience.</li>
        <li>Logout from all devices: Provides the ability for users to log out from all active sessions across different
          devices.</li>
        <li>Responsive design: Ensures the login system is compatible and optimized for different devices and screen
          sizes.</li>
